          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "As there’s no simple way to get this information from the file system the method",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "has to crawl the entire hierarchy, accumulating the overall sum on the way.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "The resulting value is roughly equivalent with the amount of bytes",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "that would become available on the volume if the directory would be deleted.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content" : [
            {
              "inlineContent" : [
                {
                  "text" : "There are a couple of oddities that are not taken into account (like symbolic links, meta data of",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
